Hello <%= @user.first_name %>,

It looks like you've just tried to change the email address associated with
your Chef user account. If you did not initiate this request, please ignore
this email. If you are indeed trying to update your account, follow
this link to confirm your new email address.

<%= email_profile_url(
  user: Base64.urlsafe_encode64({username: @user.username,  email: @email}.to_json),
  expires: @expires,
  signature: @signature).html_safe %>

Thanks,

The Chef Team
